/*--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
/* Note:                                                                                                        */
/*                                                                                                              */
/* vd_g_MemcpyU1_blp:                                                                                           */
/* - Copy loop in units of blocks of 8 bytes.                                                                   */
/* - Compared to vd_g_MemcpyU1_dw, the execution time is stable independent of alignment.                       */
/* - Although not as fast as vd_g_MemcpyU1_dw when alignment is matched, but always faster than vd_g_MemcpyU1.  */
/*   (except when copying a small amount of data, such as less than 8 bytes)                                    */
